snippet.title: Is HYBE Monopolizing Kpop?
snippet.description:
*I do not own any of the stage mix footage shown in the video, please support the official release!*

NOTE: This is a video covering  the recent release of HYBE purchasing shares/stock in SM in order to block Kakao's recent involvement. Why this is a bad or a good thing and what it really means.

Sources: https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-02-09/bts-agency-hybe-to-buy-sm-stake-joins-race-for-k-pop-pioneer

https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/skoreas-kakao-corp-buy-905-stake-sm-entertainment-touts-k-pop-projects-2023-02-07/
